data.description: FOUND YOUR DREAM ESTATE HOME WITH PLENTY OF LAND AND 2,594 sqft of living space with 3 Bedrooms, office/den, 3 Bathrooms, open concept estate home is exquisitely placed on 2.73 acres, fully fenced and gated, paved driveway, sprinkler system, with many producing fruit trees (Mango, Persimmon, Papaya, Starfruit, Graviola (Soursop), Pineapple, Sapodilla, etc., SCREEN and LANAI FRONT PORCH, NEW REVERSE OSMOSIS FILTRATION SYSTEM FOR THE ENTIRE HOUSE. THIS GEM is ready for a BIG FAMILY and is located in the coveted GOLDEN GATE ESTATES of Naples with plenty of room for a custom designed pool and guest house. Close to shopping, banks, top rated schools, dinning, and more. Don't pass up on this once in a lifetime property. ONE Owner occupied and is accepting all strong and reasonable offers. OWN this Once in a Lifetime FOREVER HOME with lots of land (2.73 ACRES) Well built and well maintained house by original owners who still occupy the property.  In an ideal part of Collier County, Naples with LOW PROPERTY TAXES, LOTS OF LAND AND TWO STREET ACCESS FOR POTENTIAL GUEST HOUSE.
